long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: You no longer need to type gibberish into your forms while developing. At the click of a button, Autofilly will fill form inputs with random, javascript generated data. Or you can use your OpenAI api key for human readable values.
